snippet.title: 100 Mind Game
snippet.description:
There is a circular grid of numbers that range between 0-100, there is also a number in the middle, the goal is to tap a number in the grid which is the same or smaller than the middle number.

You have to try and match as many numbers as you can.

This game will help improve your concentration.

Enjoy!
